entity.name: Updates on COVID-19 in Australia
entity.description: This page is a timeline of Tweets with information and advice from the prime minister, state and federal governments, health authorities and other trusted sources from around Australia. For more, visit https://www.health.gov.au/.

text: @JordanRowes doubt you'll see this.. I am a teacher and single mom of a 4 year old.  I've been out of work for the past 2 weeks due to COVID19. No food, no gas, no money. I've already overdrawn my account to the $140 limit.  I'm really questioning if we're going to survive this. https://t.co/40zRPnvnso
